lead_paragraph: Australia have chosen the experience of Peter Siddle over the potential of the uncapped Joe Mennie as their third seamer for the opening test against South Africa, which starts on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Australia Opt for Siddle in First South Africa Test
headline.main: Australia Opt for Siddle in First South Africa Test
